          "reviewBody": "One of the most commendable aspects of SSRVM  is its emphasis on values and character building. The school fosters a respectful and inclusive environment where students learn the importance of empathy, discipline, and responsibility. The consistent encouragement and support provided by the staff create an atmosphere where every student feels valued and motivated to reach their full potential.Teachers are so polite and so the principal ,always ready to help.",
